            {/* Philosophy */}
            <div className="border-l-4 border-holo-coral pl-6 my-12">
              <h2 className="text-2xl font-heading mb-4 text-holo-coral">Philosophy</h2>
              <p className="italic opacity-90">
                &quot;Ship production code at VC startup speed. Quality isn&apos;t about perfection
                — it&apos;s about continuous improvement and shipping value to users fast.&quot;
