Multiple build errors encountered and fixed:
1. PPR not available in stable Next.js - removed experimental.ppr
2. Tailwind CSS v4 requires @tailwindcss/postcss plugin
3. React 19 incompatible with R3F - downgraded to React 18
4. ESLint errors (unused imports, apostrophes, quotes)
